Class Concept

  • java.lang.Object
    • semiotic_elements.Concept
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SemioticElement

    public class Concept
extends java.lang.Object
implements SemioticElement
    A Concept is a triadic relation between the three other SemioticElements. It represents a unity of meaning in our model.
    Author:
    kemoadrian
